https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yByhHYTE5bLjAgobjC9l0dGdSKO.jpg Artisan cheese shop owner Brie finds herself competing for a $50,000 prize in her town's annual Cheese Festival. To boost her presence, she teams up with an influential cheese critic to profile her vintage smoked gouda. As their friendship develops into romance, a competitor's business proposal and unforeseen complications force Brie to put her shop - and heart - on the line. As Gouda as It Gets
